title: Light The Tires Ablaze! Week 7 Preview
description:
Welcome to the flaming inferno that separates Teams That Are Pretty Good from Teams That Nope No They Are Not. Which side will you fall on, Texas Tech and TCU? Do you dare test the power of the fire, Texas A&M and South Carolina? UCLA! Cal! You must also be tested, even if yes UCLA is kind of already burned completely at this point!
Oh, also Barry Alvarez is building a clone in full view of the world.
